        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         ExtAff doesn't affect DPS, so I'm not sure what that would accomplish.</P><P>Best test:  Find a mob of a set level.  (Gargoyles in Katta come to mind)  Snare (bring a druid or ranger for this) and root the fooker, then cast dot of choice on the mob.  Record how much damage the mob has taken after the spell wears off.  Kill it.<BR>Bring another, and repeat.  This time use the same dot with focus and check the same thing as before.</P><P>Note:  I'm pretty sure that EA items DO NOT work with darkness, and I was told by a full GM that this was intentional.</P><P>Jered Caladine<BR>Warlock of Forlorn<BR>E'ci Server<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=22847" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=22847</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
